summary: CPSC:THULE SPORT RACK BICYCLE CARRIER SPORT RACK WAS MOUNTED AS INSTRUCTED ON OUR TOYOTA. WE WERE CARRYING OUR BIKES AFTER A RIDE WHEN THE BOLT TO THE CARRIER BROKE IN HALF, PROMPTING OUR BIKES AND STEEL CARRIER TO CRASH INTO THE ROAD BEHIND US. CARRIER TO CRASH INTO THE ROAD BEHIND US. *BF  UPDATED 06/29/2017*JS
